    [
      "Pick if you like:",
      "Avoid if you dislike:"
    ],
    [
      "STRETCH 'EM: Hard knockdowns and looping pressure in and out of Prowler Stance, letting Alex maintain a terrifying offense.\r\nGood Workrate: A wide array of tools from command grabs to evasive hops to armored strikes, with even more reward on Punish Counter.\r\n20-Inch Pythons: Long-reaching pokes with great reward even at a distance.",
      "In-Ring Psychology: Recognizing when to use your options from Prowler Stance for maximum reward.\r\nGetting Cut Off: Poor reversal options barring a raw Super Art.\r\nAbnormal Throw Loop: Has to use Drive Rush or enter Prowler Stance in order to throw loop properly, telegraphing Alex's intentions more than other characters."
    ]
  ],
