    [
      "Assist Combos",
      "A[L~L]: 5LK ~ L Flash Axe\r\n5/2L~A[2L~L~L]: 5LP/2LK ~ 2LK ~ 2LP ~ L Flash Axe\r\nVariant ender that lets Alex get a Light Assist Combo from a chained starter\r\nA[M~M~M]: 2MP ~ OD Flash Chop ~ SA2\r\nBurnout: 2MP ~ L Flash Axe\r\nOn Block: stops at OD Flash Chop/M Flash Axe\r\nSA2 cancel will occur on 1st hit of OD Flash Chop if not delayed\r\nA[H (hold)~H~H]: 5HP (hold) ~ H Flash Chop ~ SA3\r\nNo SA3: cancels into Collapsing Driver (4MK) instead\r\nTo perform Power Drop, stop the Assist Combo and perform it with 4S or 63214X\r\nOn Block: stops at H Flash Chop\r\nNo Assist Combo will come out if the initial A[H] is uncharged"
    ],
    [
      "Miscellaneous Changes",
      "2L is 2LK but switches to 2LP if chained into\r\n2LP is unavailable outside of chains\r\nThis limits Modern Alex's 5-frame punish game, with 2L~2H being the most consistent option"
    ]
